data.description: Townhomes of Grande Lagoon! Conveniently located a mile from Big Lagoon State Park and the Southwest Public Library. Minutes from the Beaches of Perdido Key and near NAS Pensacola, TARGET, WALMART, PUBLIX, & ALDI. Upstairs this property has two bedrooms, each with it's own bath & a half bath on the first floor. There is a nice privacy fenced back patio, great for entertaining and family cookouts! Freshly painted throughout & new carpet upstairs. Roof in 2021, Windows in 2022, Hot Water Heater in 2023. Vacant on combo lockbox, so very easy to show! (room dimensions are approximate and should be verified by the buyer)
